## Common Operations

### Pull Requests
```bash
gh pr list                                    # List PRs
gh pr view <number>                           # View PR details
gh pr create --title "..." --body "..."      # Create PR
gh pr checkout <number>                       # Checkout PR branch
gh pr review <number> --approve               # Approve PR
gh pr merge <number>                          # Merge PR
gh pr diff <number>                           # View PR diff
```

### Issues
```bash
gh issue list                                 # List issues
gh issue view <number>                        # View issue
gh issue create --title "..." --body "..."   # Create issue
gh issue close <number>                       # Close issue
```

### Repository
```bash
gh repo view                                  # View repo info
gh repo clone <repo>                          # Clone repository
gh repo fork                                  # Fork repository
```

### Workflows (CI/CD Debugging)
```bash
gh workflow list                              # List workflows
gh workflow view <workflow>                   # View workflow details
gh run list                                   # List workflow runs
gh run view <run-id>                          # View run logs
gh run view <run-id> --log                    # Full logs
gh run view <run-id> --log-failed             # Failed job logs only
gh run rerun <run-id>                         # Rerun failed workflow
```

