## Usage Examples

### Debug Failed Workflow:
```bash
gh run list --workflow=deploy.yml --limit=5
gh run view <run-id> --log-failed
```

### Create PR with Context:
```bash
gh pr create --title "feat(agents): add custom tool" \
  --body "Implements custom tool support\n\nCloses #123"
```

### Review PR Changes:
```bash
gh pr diff <number>
gh pr checks <number>
gh pr review <number> --comment --body "LGTM"
```

